729906f-a.text:
William Street, at Jackson Street (foreground), looking northwestward across the S.E. corner of the two streets. The 21N-story white house is No. 63 William Street, at the N.E. corner of Brewster Street and was owned by G. W. Rathburn in 1874.
May 28, 1927
P. L. Sperr
